{"tid":909771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（飛來橫禍）第一次帶女朋友見父母 ，發現佢係我阿妹","createTime":"2018-11-20T15:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T16:19:02.000Z","uid":142518,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"af2554b84748f1d2d45075dd25e22da37a252004","tid":909771,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:40:53.000Z","msg":"話說今日第一次帶女朋友返屋企見我父母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我           <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：女朋友    <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我老豆       <br />\n  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：老豆老母，佢係我女朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：伯父伯母你地好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：而家做緊咩㗎，今年幾歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我做護士架，今年25<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：幾好喎，咁你爸爸媽媽做盛行？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我單親家庭長大㗎，我媽媽都係護士，不過我係威爾斯做，佢係廣華<br />\n <br />\n呢個時候老竇突然抬高頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你姓咩？係咪跟啊媽姓？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我姓邱，全名叫邱xx，跟阿媽。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你地住邊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我地住彩虹邨<br />\n<br />\n之後老竇全程都冇講嘢，<br />\n女朋友走咗之後我老竇靜靜雞同我講，<br />\n佢好有可能係我阿妹。佢話我三歲果時<br />\n有一次同老母鬧大交，出咗去搵一個鍾意佢嘅女仔談心，飲大咗兩杯仲搞大埋人哋個肚，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個女仔唔落左佢，而且冇叫老竇負責任<br />\n<br />\n咁之後佢哋就冇咗聯絡，<br />\n咁啱個女仔又係姓白，時間計落又係25歲<br />\n雖然之前唔係住彩虹邨，但係佢嘅機會率好大<br />\n最重要係老母唔知<br />\n<br />\n依家老竇叫我睇吓佢老母係咪真係嗰個女仔<br />\n佢俾咗個名俾我，但係我唔敢問我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f762a7e81678bbaefc8708bc70759ed8e366fbf","tid":909771,"uid":25391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"740d36511178cbe4411fa555e7e6d5707229262a","tid":909771,"uid":6946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0d669aeacd47c2aa7abbc92cf4a878ab9d7a65f8","tid":909771,"uid":86266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"打和"},{"pid":"4c2c9a61e848505623e13a083282dd858139514d","tid":909771,"uid":177089,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"姓邱定白"},{"pid":"0d8b6c6de953682b865089f6984fe7dde4617c69","tid":909771,"uid":69083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"0.1/10, 分數係比你d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28be6c8777a38e013cd29dfb680c1b7f6b14de22","tid":909771,"uid":135445,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"姓白又姓邱??????????????????????????????<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d4a99179ce5643ca5388e9165b0c1e080e7a67","tid":909771,"uid":28741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"雷雨劇場"},{"pid":"47501a1b7d6e0ddccafb539fbd23bcdfb11d17fe","tid":909771,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:53:08.000Z","msg":"錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a99109bc34b497d7f4bbd2ee94f07af9be71b29","tid":909771,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"姓邱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/n